Package: macrosyntR
Type: Package
Title: This package plots oxford grided plots showing the macrosynteny conservation between two species
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sami El Hilali
Maintainer: Sami El Hilali <elhilali.sami@gmail.com>
Description: This package is intended to serialize the plotting of oxford grided plot for chromosomal evolution studies. The orthologs (mutual best hits) have to be computed beforehand (using for example the bashscript : https://github.com/SamiLhll/GenomicUtils/blob/a8803782f64c7ff31f0723d9e11f8f7d1a57e907/MacroSynteny/Generate_blastp_MBH).
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/SamiLhll/macrosyntR
BugReports: https://github.com/SamiLhll/macrosyntR/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
